                        <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18410920-2511-offence-1 t18410920-geo-11"></join>Camberwell</placeName>, and stealing therein, 9 spoons, value 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 14<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 pair of Sugar-tongs, value 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 watch-guard, value 12<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 watch, value 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 4 shillings, and 1 farthing; the property of <persName id="t18410920-name-949" type="victimName">
